              We know you have an individual taste and style, and we know you’re creative, thats why you’re in the beauty business, obvs. So we give you some customisable templates, fun animations and make it super responsive across mobile applications.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2">
          <h4 class="green-text">MONETIZE YOUR SOCIAL CONTENT</h4>
          <div class="brief">
